data.name: EmailAddress_Description
data.value: The EmailAddress scalar type represents a email address, represented as UTF-8 character sequences. The scalar follows the specification defined in RFC 5322

data.name: EmailAddress_IsInvalid_ParseLiteral
data.value: EmailAddress cannot parse the provided literal. The provided value does not meet the RFC 5322 specification.

data.name: EmailAddress_IsInvalid_ParseValue
data.value: EmailAddress cannot parse the provided value. The provided value does not meet the RFC 5322 specification.

data.name: NegativeIntType_Description
data.value: The NegativeIntType scalar type represents a signed 32-bit numeric non-fractional with a maximum of -1.

data.name: NegativeIntType_IsNotNegative_ParseLiteral
data.value: NegativeIntType cannot parse the provided literal. The provided value was not negative.

data.name: NegativeIntType_IsNotNegative_ParseValue
data.value: NegativeIntType cannot parse the provided value. The provided value was not negative.
